pepe the bull is a 2002 american animated television film produced by walt disney productions and released by buena vista distribution company . the film was directed by arturo &lt;unk&gt; and written by jorge r. &lt;unk&gt; . the film was released in the united states on december 15 , 2002 . the film was nominated for the academy award for best animated short film at the 37th academy awards , but was not nominated .